-- Itatile South Africa Company Plane Reported Missing Near Plettenberg Bay
-- B y   S i k o n a t h i   M a n t s h a n t s h a
-- 2011-02-09T05:31:12Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-09/itatile-south-africa-company-plane-reported-missing-near-plettenberg-bay.html
A plane belonging to  Italtile Ltd ., a
South African ceramic-tile retailer, was missing near
Plettenberg Bay on the nation’s south coast, Chief Financial
Officer Peter Swatton said.  The craft was carrying “predominantly staff members,”
Swatton said by phone from Johannesburg today. He declined to
provide further information.  “We are currently counselling family members of those
involved,” he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sikonathi Mantshantsha in Johannesburg at 
